OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772019653
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin two-day Jordan
OL,4,Cvisit to highlight humanitarian efforts
OL,6,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex will
OL,7,Fbegin a two-day visit to Jordan to
OL,8,Fhighlight efforts to support
OL,9,Fvulnerable communities affected by
OL,10,Fconflict and displacement.
OL,12,FHarry and Meghan will also visit
OL,13,Finitiatives they have helped fund to
OL,14,Fmedically evacuate children from the
OL,15,Fwar in Gaza to the Middle East nation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
