OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772019653
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin two-day Jordan
OL,4,Cvisit to highlight humanitarian efforts
OL,6,FThe couple, who stepped down as
OL,7,Fworking royals in 2020 for personal
OL,8,Fand financial freedom, are travelling
OL,9,Fto Jordan at the invitation of Dr
OL,10,FTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, director-
OL,11,Fgeneral of the World Health
OL,12,FOrganisation (WHO).
OL,14,FTheir visit comes at time of crisis
OL,15,Ffor the royal family following the
OL,16,Farrest of Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor
OL,17,Fon suspicion of misconduct in public
OL,18,Foffice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
