OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772019653
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin two-day Jordan
OL,4,Cvisit to highlight humanitarian efforts
OL,6,FHarry has not spoken publicly about
OL,7,Fthe turmoil that has engulfed his
OL,8,Frelatives, but in his memoir Spare he
OL,9,Fwrote how despite his uncle Andrew
OL,10,Ffacing allegations of sexual assault
OL,11,Fin connection with convicted
OL,12,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein, there was
OL,13,Fno suggestion he lose his taxpayer-
OL,14,Ffunded security.
OL,16,FIn May last year the duke lost a Court
OL,17,Fof Appeal challenge over his security
OL,18,Farrangements while in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
