PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772019653
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin two-day Jordan
OL,4,Cvisit to highlight humanitarian efforts
OL,6,FBut in a major U-turn, the Home Office
OL,7,Fis said to have now ordered a full
OL,8,Fthreat assessment for the first time
OL,9,Fsince 2020, amid reports Harry's
OL,10,Ftaxpayer-funded armed protection will
OL,11,Fbe reinstated for visits to the UK.
OL,13,FSince moving to California in 2020 for
OL,14,Fa new life the Sussexes have carried
OL,15,Fout a number of foreign visits that
OL,16,Fhave taken the form of official trips
OL,17,Fthey made when still part of 'The
OL,18,FFirm' as the royal family is
OL,19,Fcolloquially known.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
