OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772019653
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin two-day Jordan
OL,4,Cvisit to highlight humanitarian efforts
OL,6,FDuring their two-day visit the
OL,7,FSussexes will meet Jordanian leaders
OL,8,Fand senior health officials, engage
OL,9,Fwith WHO teams, visit frontline health
OL,10,Fand mental health programmes and meet
OL,11,FWorld Central Kitchen staff co-
OL,12,Fordinating food relief for Gaza from
OL,13,FAmman.
OL,15,FThey will also visit the social
OL,16,Fdevelopment organisation Questscope's
OL,17,Fyouth centre to hear from young people
OL,18,Fparticipating in creative and
OL,19,Fwellbeing programmes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
