OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin two-day Jordan
OL,4,Cvisit to highlight humanitarian efforts
OL,6,FThe couple first partnered with the
OL,7,FWHO on a global campaign to encourage
OL,8,Fvaccine equity and co-hosted a high-
OL,9,Flevel event at the UN General Assembly
OL,10,Fin 2021, and their charitable body has
OL,11,Falso worked with the organisation on
OL,12,Fits global initiative to help end
OL,13,Fviolence against children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
